            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                D<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ositio</ex></expan> Luciani su<expan><ex>b</ex><abbr>d</abbr><ex>iaconi</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>VIIII &amp;lt;K=X&amp;gt;(alendas) <expan><abbr>Septemb</abbr><ex>res</ex></expan> Di<lb break="no" n="3"/>oscoro <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> d<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ositio</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Thalasi <expan><abbr>Id</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Maximo II et <lb n="6"/>Paterio </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Depositio Criscenti <lb n="2"/>VII <expan><abbr>Id</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Septemb</abbr><ex>res</ex></expan> indictio<lb break="no" n="3"/>ne XI qui vixit annos <lb n="4"/>XVIII Dioscoro <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Bestattungsdaten der drei im Sarkophag beigesetzten Personen: Lucianus 24.8.442, Criscentius 7.9.442, Thalasius 13.8.443. Zwei aneinander passende Fragmente eines Sarkophagkastens.</p>
